</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/8b744eb1317603fabdc12e64d10d5f12?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/jxblum">John Blum</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2019-08-23 19:09:33.528">August 23, 2019</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="3779" href="/blog/2019/08/23/spring-boot-for-apache-geode-pivotal-gemfire-1-1-0-release-1-2-0-m1-released#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><div class="paragraph">
<p>On behalf of the Spring and Apache Geode communities, it is my pleasure to announce the release of <em>Spring Boot for Apache Geode &amp; Pivotal GemFire</em> (SBDG) <code>1.1.0.RELEASE</code> and the <code>1.2.0.M1</code> release.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>SBDG <code>1.1.0.RELEASE</code> is available in <a href="https://search.maven.org/search?q=spring-geode-starter">Maven Central</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>SBDG <code>1.2.0.M1</code> is available in the <a href="https://repo.spring.io/milestone/org/springframework/geode/spring-geode-starter/1.2.0.M1/">Spring Milestone</a> repository.</p>
</div>
<h1 id="whats-new-120M1" class="sect0"><a class="anchor" href="#whats-new-120M1"></a>Whatâ€™s New in <code>1.2.0.M1</code></h1>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><em>Spring Boot for Apache Geode &amp; Pivotal GemFire</em> (SBDG) <code>1.2.0.M1</code> was a baseline release to align SBDG on latest GemFire/Geode and Spring bits:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li> <p>Spring Framework 5.2.0.RC1</p> </li>
<li> <p>Spring Boot 2.2.0.M5</p> </li>
<li> <p>Spring Data Moore-RC2/2.2.0.RC2</p> </li>
<li> <p>Spring Session Corn-M3/2.2.0.M3</p> </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</section>
